Package: ChocoPhlAnTaxonomies
Type: Package
Title: ChocoPhlAn Taxonomies, Trees and Tables
Description: A package to manipulate taxonomy and phylogenetic data from several
    MetaPhlAn and ChocoPhlAn versions. This is a more targeted utility package 
    that used to be in `g-antonello/ChocoPhlAnTaxonomies`. It provides a uniform and 
    public source of taxonomy and phylogenetic trees from publicly available 
    ChocoPhlAn versions.
Version: 0.5.0
